node.title: Teen Palmerston North boy missing, police ask for help
node.description: Kamera Harris was last seen on January 2.
node.content: ["Police are asking for the public's help in finding a missing 15-year-old.", "Kamera Harris was last seen on January 2 in Palmerston North.\u00a0", "\"Given his age and the amount of time that has passed, police are concerned about his welfare and are asking anyone who may have seen Kamera or has information on his whereabouts to please contact Police urgently on 111,\" police say.", "In the missing person notification to media, police ask people not to approach Harris, but rather phone 111 immediately if they see him.", "Anyone who may know where he is or can provide other information is also asked to phone the police.", "\"It's important that anyone with information on Kamera's whereabouts contacts police as we want to ensure he is safe,\" police say.", "Harris has family in Masterton and Northland, so police say there is a possibility he has travelled to these regions."]
